column5: Some fishing video taken over the last year.
Great work Iceguy! Need to add some hot carpin' action.
Wow!!!  That was awsome!  Nice job and thanks for the entertainment   Don
Sweet Reels Thanks for sharing !!!!!!
That was a great video!  Better than some fishing shows I've seen.  Great job!
Nice!!
What Cliff said.  Well done.
Nice video!  Makes me glad I'm heading up with some buddies on the weekend...
Great Vid! I gotta figure out how to do that!!!!!
Very cool - nice editing job.  I just hope this doesn't mean we're coming to the end of the season
Very nice  Have you hugged a salmon today  Thanks for sharing!

Cool Fishing Video !!!!!! well done,  thats a great idea,taking videos of all the big fish you have caught all year long   ,thanks for sharing,and for the idea,i might try that next year as well....cheers
Well done, good music too...I wasn't bored.
nice one
Thank's guy I hope to put more out in the near future, Hey Rod Im saving the carp for the sucker,carp,sheepshead video.
That was really good .

honestly Rob that was an awesome video...Good fishing with good budys...cant beat that...hope you can come out on my reading week for some fall action...PS. tried to put a comment on utube but didnt have a username so it wouldnt let me....
Great job buddy! Looks like you've had a great season so far.
Hey, don't forget the Hot Goby Action....
We'll save that for the asian carp, spiny water flea,goby video. Making a salmon one now. Would like to make a Ottawa river edition this weekend but the stars have to be on the line..

That video was so cool!!! Great fishing days with buddies. cant wait to hit the Big River again. I heard about you trip with SnagmasterAl should be fun.  speaking for everyone on the board, We want another ICEGUY productions Video.  Good job rob
I was impressed
